long_description: Fairing for Yakima car racks reduces wind noise and increases fuel efficiency by making your rack more aerodynamic-great place for stickers, too! 32" fairing fits vehicles similar in size to Subaru Outback Wagon and Toyota Sienna. Tool-free installation; integrated snaparounds make installation onto round bars a breeze. Protective bumpers won't damage paint. Lockable with SKS lock housings and cores (sold separately). Car rack sold separately.
